data.description: BRING AN OFFER! Welcome to your new home that backs up to a beautiful pond!! Roof is only a few years old, HVAC replaced in 2021, air ducts just cleaned, and gas water heater replaced November 2023! Located just minutes to NAS Pensacola and a short drive to Downtown Pensacola, this four bedroom, two bathroom home boasts nearly 2,000 square feet of interior space. Inside features and open floorplan living room, dining area, and eat-in kitchen all connected by flowing LVP floors and tall ceilings. In the living room you'll find a cozy gas fireplace and vaulted ceilings with plant ledge details. From there is access to the screened porch with gorgeous views of the water beyond. It's the perfect place to sit with a morning cup of coffee or unwind in the evening without pesky mosquitos. The living room opens up into the eat-in kitchen with a long breakfast bar for casual dining and a huge pantry/laundry combo. Split from the guest bedrooms and bathroom is the private primary suite. With views of the pond and an amazing ensuite bathroom, it's a true oasis. Speaking of the primary bath, it features double sinks with a makeup vanity, his and hers walk-in closets, and a soaking tub! Out back is a fully privacy fenced yard and a separate fenced area for the dogs. The back gate opens up to the pond and when the temps finally cool down, there's a firepit for roasting s'mores!
